{"tid":1662623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］拯救維尼 Free Hong Kong  Save Winnie!","createTime":"2019-10-19T01:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T02:09:17.000Z","uid":214298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86fabd710af289816e4bba479b86a6ef02af581c","tid":1662623,"uid":214298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:25:43.000Z","msg":"［借帳問］［集思廣益］<br />\n是咁的，這是和我朝夕相處的維尼。我唔明點解因為佢個樣生得似習近平，就成日畀你地糟質，一時又打七佢一時又畀火燒咁，其實佢乜都冇做過。我覺得佢好慘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其係無論你點糟質佢，佢都係會對你報以天真爛漫的微笑。每一次返到屋企見到佢，我就覺得好內疚。我相信香港有唔少人同我一樣，都愛護維尼。<br />\n<br />\n我想巴打絲打幫下手，搞個「<span style=\"font-size: large;\">與維尼同行</span>」集會，大家帶維尼出來，證明佢都係fight for freedom, stand with Hong Kong 免佢再受皮肉之苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXGBz8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXGBz8b.jpg&h=da18d43a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqycSUT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqycSUT.jpg&h=a769cb79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5QOreV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5QOreV.jpg&h=50a5d8d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bda894c7de51b0ec244f3a1aec36b1c97a0bc50","tid":1662623,"uid":273531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"89b4ce83123790d44d8c53147515eeec48d867f5","tid":1662623,"uid":273531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86fabd710af289816e4bba479b86a6ef02af581c","tid":1662623,"uid":214298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:25:43.000Z","msg":"［借帳問］［集思廣益］<br />\n是咁的，這是和我朝夕相處的維尼。我唔明點解因為佢個樣生得似習近平，就成日畀你地糟質，一時又打七佢一時又畀火燒咁，其實佢乜都冇做過。我覺得佢好慘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其係無論你點糟質佢，佢都係會對你報以天真爛漫的微笑。每一次返到屋企見到佢，我就覺得好內疚。我相信香港有唔少人同我